    <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

    <p><strong>How do puzzles work?</strong><br>
    Fill every cell with one of two symbols. No more than two of the same symbol can sit side by side, and every row/column must contain an equal number of each symbol. Special "=" and "×" clues tell you when two cells must match or differ.</p>

    <p><strong>I ran out of hints. What do I do?</strong><br>
    Watch a short rewarded ad to earn an extra hint, or purchase a puzzle pack from the Shop for more puzzles and hints.</p>

    <p><strong>How do I remove ads?</strong><br>
    Go to Shop and purchase any "Flex" pack, or the standalone "No Ads" option. This removes all ads permanently on your account.</p>

    <p><strong>I made a purchase but didn't receive my content.</strong><br>
    Please make sure you're connected to the internet when completing a purchase. If the issue persists, contact us below with your purchase receipt/date and we'll help right away.</p>

    <p><strong>How do I change the app language or theme?</strong><br>
    Go to Settings from the main menu to change language, icon set, theme (White / Teal / Night), and sound/vibration preferences.</p>

